            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "Minimal repro:\n```lua\nlocal _msg_buf = vim.api.nvim_create_buf(false, false)\nvim.api.nvim_buf_set_text(_msg_buf, 0, 0, 0, 0, { \"Hello World\" })\nvim.cmd.tabnew()\nlocal _msg_win =\n\tvim.api.nvim_open_win(_msg_buf, false, { relative = \"editor\", width = 20, height = 1, row = 0, col = 0 })\nvim.cmd.normal(\"ZQ\")\n-- vim.cmd([[tabclose!]])\nvim.print(vim.api.nvim_buf_get_lines(_msg_buf, 0, -1, false))\n```",
